   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a1e1cf60-6952-423b-b81c-858b53be67e0",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Error Analysis & Root Cause Analysis (RCA)\n",
    "\n",
    "### False Positives\n",
    "False positives occur when genuine transactions are incorrectly classified as fraud.\n",
    "\n",
    "### False Negatives\n",
    "False negatives occur when fraudulent transactions are classified as genuine.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Reasons for Model Failure\n",
    "- Extreme class imbalance\n",
    "- Overlapping fraud and non-fraud patterns\n",
    "\n",
    "### Corrective Strategies\n",
    "- Threshold tuning\n",
    "- SMOTE oversampling\n"
   ]
  },
